16:49.788 --> 16:51.522
Are you slut shaming me?

16:51.557 --> 16:52.559
No.

16:54.193 --> 16:55.959
Here she comes.

16:55.995 --> 16:58.162
- Hi.
- Hi.

16:58.197 --> 17:01.265
- Can I have another Alice?
- Of course, coming right up.

17:01.300 --> 17:02.833
Thank you.

17:02.868 --> 17:04.334
Come here, my friends.

17:04.369 --> 17:06.103
- Hey, I have a question.
- Mm-hmm?

17:06.137 --> 17:07.671
What the f...
do you think you're doing here?

17:07.705 --> 17:09.173
Not leaving until we get our money.

17:09.208 --> 17:10.707
I already told you. There's no money.

17:10.742 --> 17:12.509
Well, then I guess you better get it.

17:14.046 --> 17:15.512
Well, that dude Patrick
is clearly loaded.

17:15.548 --> 17:17.047
How long till you steal all his money?

17:17.082 --> 17:18.315
You can pay us then.

17:18.349 --> 17:20.284
