- Oh.

17:20.319 --> 17:21.852
Okay, how about this?

17:21.887 --> 17:23.921
You think you three bozos
can keep your shit together

17:23.955 --> 17:25.722
for about 30 minutes?

17:25.758 --> 17:27.257
We're not having trouble
keeping our shit together.

17:27.292 --> 17:29.526
Precisely, exactly, boom.

17:29.562 --> 17:31.261
Okay, I'm cutting you off.

17:31.297 --> 17:32.796
- Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.
- I'm cutting you off.

17:32.831 --> 17:35.032
So what happens in 30 minutes?

17:35.067 --> 17:37.134
Max gets here and tells
you all about your money.

17:37.169 --> 17:38.735
Good, look forward to that.

17:38.771 --> 17:42.039
- One Alice, made with love.
- Thank you.

17:42.074 --> 17:43.473
Stop it.

17:48.314 --> 17:49.880
So who the hell is Max?

17:49.915 --> 17:52.115
No idea.

17:56.589 --> 17:58.155
Oh, yeah.

