18:22.481 --> 18:24.514
<i>and Jules Langmore.</i>

18:24.550 --> 18:26.250
Son of a bitch.

18:26.285 --> 18:27.651
- How... how did they...
- I don't know.

18:27.686 --> 18:29.219
I don't know. Just get here.

18:42.558 --> 18:44.809
Legion of Boom. '85 Bears.

18:44.844 --> 18:47.845
- Game-defining D.
- Oh, absolutely game-defining.

18:47.880 --> 18:49.513
Played a little ball
back in high school.

18:49.549 --> 18:51.448
I'm certainly glad I didn't have to face

18:51.484 --> 18:53.083
any of those super smart secondaries.

18:53.119 --> 18:54.318
Right, well, who would?

18:54.353 --> 18:55.586
I played too.

18:55.621 --> 18:57.154
Quarterback.

18:57.190 --> 18:59.304
- Aw, really?
- Hell yeah, man.

19:00.793 --> 19:02.493
Well, here you go.

19:02.528 --> 19:03.861
- Perfect.
- Yeah, cheers, bro.

19:03.896 --> 19:07.531
Game time. Thank you.

19:07.567 --> 19:08.966
New boy crush?

19:09.001 --> 19:10.601
He seems like a good guy.

