19:12.638 --> 19:14.004
Blah, bloo, blee, bloops.

19:14.040 --> 19:15.840
Okay, drink some water.

19:16.876 --> 19:18.375
Drink it, okay?

19:18.411 --> 19:20.213
Can I please have everyone's attention?

19:21.714 --> 19:25.349
Old friends, new friends, family.

19:25.384 --> 19:27.618
I wanna thank everyone
for being here tonight

19:27.653 --> 19:30.554
