19:41.346 --> 19:43.968
And I thought, "Now this is
a woman that isn't gonna"

19:44.003 --> 19:45.536
take any of my shit."

19:46.906 --> 19:48.172
I like that.

19:48.207 --> 19:49.173
We do too.

19:51.010 --> 19:53.344
- You know, I have a saying...
- Oh, he has his own saying.

19:53.379 --> 19:56.380
When love is the answer,

19:56.415 --> 19:58.082
doesn't matter what the question is.

19:58.117 --> 20:00.017
It's kind of cool,
but does that qualify as a saying?

20:00.052 --> 20:01.919
- No, it does not.
- Shh.

20:01.954 --> 20:04.054
The last few years have presented me

20:04.090 --> 20:07.658
