the way you challenge me,

20:24.210 --> 20:26.543
all of it.

20:26.579 --> 20:27.912
To Saffron.

20:28.047 --> 20:29.346
To Saffron.

20:30.783 --> 20:32.416
Can I puke now or later?

20:32.451 --> 20:34.084
Aw, it was a pretty good speech,
though, overall.

20:34.120 --> 20:37.755
Poor sap, he has no idea what's coming.

20:37.790 --> 20:39.957
