20:51.760 --> 20:53.070
Oh, you gotta be kidding me.

20:53.105 --> 20:54.104
Oh, wow.

20:57.576 --> 20:59.243
Yeah.

21:12.925 --> 21:14.358
Ooh.

21:25.104 --> 21:26.170
Cheers.

21:28.708 --> 21:29.940
Hey, brother.

21:31.444 --> 21:33.610
Hey, you know, money talks...

21:33.646 --> 21:35.779
Wanna dance?

21:35.815 --> 21:37.481
