24:55.381 --> 24:57.581
Okay, then I just like
the way you smell.

25:03.422 --> 25:05.589
Excuse me, ma'am. More champagne?

25:05.624 --> 25:07.057
What?

25:07.092 --> 25:08.458
I saw you dancing with Ezra out there.

25:08.494 --> 25:09.793
I need a one-on-one too, okay?

25:09.828 --> 25:11.962
One-on-one what?

25:11.997 --> 25:14.464
Meet me upstairs in the
study in five minutes.

25:14.500 --> 25:15.866
- Richard.
- Or I'm gonna go big.

25:15.901 --> 25:17.935
Richard.

25:17.970 --> 25:19.581
Do it.

25:20.806 --> 25:24.241
What? You can't be serious.

25:24.276 --> 25:25.642
I'm serious, okay? I need closure

25:25.678 --> 25:27.411
really, really, really, really badly,

25:27.446 --> 25:30.278
and this is the only way I can do it.

25:31.984 --> 25:34.751
If I do this, do you promise
to get the hell out of Seattle?

25:34.787 --> 25:38.722
- Yes, yes, yes, okay?
- Fine, five minutes.

25:38.757 --> 25:40.424
Okay.

25:40.857 --> 25:41.725
Dumbass.

25:53.288 --> 25:55.555
Hello, Richard.

25:58.893 --> 26:00.092
Alice.

26:14.542 --> 26:16.208
How've you been?

26:16.244 --> 26:18.975
I'm fine, thank you.

26:20.481 --> 26:22.219
Look, we need to talk.

26:23.418 --> 26:26.552
It's not gonna be easy,
but I need you to hear this.

26:26.588 --> 26:29.188
- Should I take a seat?
- Just... let me...

26:29.223 --> 26:31.223
- I was gonna say that.
- Oh, I'm sorry.

26:31.259 --> 26:32.458
Go ahead.

26:34.829 --> 26:37.797
Uh, have a seat.

26:39.100 --> 26:41.601
- Thank you.
- Yeah.

26:49.944 --> 26:52.912
