and you can't come with me.

27:38.226 --> 27:40.960
- Maybe if...
- Just... just don't, please.

27:40.995 --> 27:43.429
Please, seriously.

27:46.534 --> 27:49.268
You know,
sometimes I can't eat or sleep.

27:49.303 --> 27:51.771
