and so I'm...

28:03.384 --> 28:07.953
I'm breaking up with you,
and, uh, we're done.

28:07.989 --> 28:10.890
You understand?

28:10.925 --> 28:12.525
We're done.

28:12.560 --> 28:14.186
Go.

28:16.263 --> 28:17.963
Please.

28:29.331 --> 28:31.117
I'm sorry.

