It's my job. I told you.

29:12.120 --> 29:14.653
- Well, it's a shit job, okay?
- Ugh.

29:14.689 --> 29:17.089
Boo to your job.

29:18.659 --> 29:20.459
Oh! Hey.

29:20.495 --> 29:23.596
- There you go.
