30:20.885 --> 30:24.419
with each person that we meet.

30:24.455 --> 30:31.059
Our birthday girl, 30 years, or 30 days.

30:32.863 --> 30:38.367
Maybe we should all just face the facts,
that Saffron Keyes

30:38.402 --> 30:40.035
- is really just...
